'''Kenneth Wayne "Ken" Smith''' (born July 12, 1953) is an American former professional [[basketball]] player.<ref name=bbr>{{cite web | url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/s/smithke02.html | title=Ken Smith ABA & NBA stats| publisher=Sports Reference LLC | work=basketball-reference.com | accessdate=October 15, 2014}}</ref> He played in the [[American Basketball Association]] for the [[San Antonio Spurs]] at the beginning of the 1975<U+2013>76 season.<ref name=bbr/>

